    <h1>Frequently asked Questions</h1>

   <h6 id=FAQs>How do I create an account?</h6>

       <p id="FAQa"> Click on "Create new account" on the navbar. Enter information requested in the text boxes. Press the submit button. If the information is left blank there will be an error. A new account will not be created with out the information requested. </p>

       <h6 id="FAQs">How do I log in as a customer?</h6>

        <p id="FAQa">Click on  "Log In" on the navbar. Enter username and password. If the incorrect username or password is entered, you will receive an error notification.</p>

        <h6 id="FAQs">How do I log in as a employee?</h6>

        <p id="FAQa">Click on "Employee Login" on the footer. Enter username and password. If the incorrect username or password is entered, you will
        receive an error notification.</p>

        <h6 id="FAQs">How do I place an order if I have an account?</h6>

        <p id="FAQa">Click on the tiles on the home page (if you're not sure where the home page is, or if you're not sure if you're on the home page, click on "Home" on the navbar.) Log in to your account. Select what you want to purchase and enter the quantity of product you want to purchase. After you complete your shopping and are ready to check out, click "Cart" on the navbar. Click on "Proceed to checkout" on bottom right of page. Once on the checkout page, confirm the payment and address information and click the "submit" button. </p>

        <h6 id="FAQs">How do I palce an order if I do NOT have an account?</h6>
        <p id="FAQa">Click on the tiles on the home page (if you're not sure where the home page is, or if you're not sure if you're on the
        home page, click on "Home" on the navbar.) Enter the quantity of product you want to purchase. After you complete your
        shopping and are ready to check out, click "Cart" on the navbar. Click on "Proceed to checkout" on bottom right of page. Enter all your information and click on "submit" to compete the order.</p>

        <h6 id="FAQs">How do I change my account information?</h6>
        <p id="FAQa">Log in to your account and go to information page. Select information you want to change and enter update/new information. Click the "Update" button.</p>

        <h6 id="FAQs">How do I search for products?</h6>
        <p id="FAQa">Locate the search bar in the navbar. Enter the name of the product you wish to locate. Press enter. If nothing comes back, then we either don't have the product, or we have it under a different name.</p>

